{"title":"心里的话就是诗","authors":["康?"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里的话就是诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"康?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把江南搬华北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担山抬水推湖泊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把江南搬华北；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶造轮船赶挂帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺风华北过江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤粮食万斤薯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤粮食万斤薯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空闲片地点瓜子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四肥四水七锄麦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功夫赛过绣花女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水土果木养山坡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锛石头，砍山头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开泉凿井挖渠沟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山坡上，鱼鳞坑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果木花椒和杨柳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龟背盖起花果山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山坡水土不流走；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天雨地泉咱们管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果木年年大丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）“龟背”是大王店乡一座山的名字，如今这里人民已给改名叫“花果山”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}